               <p>MR. PHILLIPS conducted the prosecution.</p>
               <p>SOLOMON BALLIN. I am a glass-cutter, and live in Rosoman-street, Clerkenwell. 
               
                  <persName id="t18310630-179-victim1325" type="victimName">
                     Michael 
