                  </persName>
            . Q. Are you quite certain your brother-in-law was alive fifteen years ago, at all events? A. Oh, yes, but I did not know that the prisoner was alive till last Monday.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310630-179-person1331">
                  THOMAS 
                  FARLEY
               <interp inst="t18310630-179-person1331" type="surname" value="FARLEY"></interp>
